'''Force travel''' was a [[Force power/Legends|Force power]] which allowed a being to travel great distances instantly by creating a momentary rift in space. This power caused the user to be corrupted by the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]], as it broke the normal rules of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] by ripping [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] asunder. The technique became more corrupting to use depending both on how far away the target was, as well as how familiar the Force-user was with the location.

